-*- texinfo -*-
@deftypefn {Mapping Function} {} pow2 (@var{x})
@deftypefnx {Mapping Function} {} pow2 (@var{f}, @var{e})
With one argument, computes
@iftex
@tex
 $2^x$
@end tex
@end iftex
@ifinfo
 2 .^ x
@end ifinfo
for each element of @var{x}.  With two arguments, returns
@iftex
@tex
 $f \cdot 2^e$.
@end tex
@end iftex
@ifinfo
 f .* (2 .^ e).
@end ifinfo
@seealso{nextpow2}
@end deftypefn
